ute;n Ã„Æ’n ng&agrave;y thÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»ï¿½ng nhÃ†Â° rau luÃ¡Â»â„¢c, dÃ†Â°a c&agrave; v.v.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>CÃ¡Â»â€” c&uacute;ng tÃ¡Â»â€¢ ti&ecirc;n</h3>\r\n<p>C&uacute;ng tÃ¡Â»â€¢ ti&ecirc;n (ng&agrave;y giÃ¡Â»â€” chÃ¡ÂºÂ¡p, ng&agrave;y tÃ¡ÂºÂ¿t cÃ¡Â»â€¢ truyÃ¡Â»ï¿½n) thÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»ï¿½ng sÃ¡Â»Â­ dÃ¡Â»Â¥ng x&ocirc;i Ã„â€˜Ã¡ÂºÂ­u xanh, x&ocirc;i gÃ¡ÂºÂ¥c vÃ¡Â»â€ºi g&agrave; luÃ¡Â»â„¢c nguy&ecirc;n con hoÃ¡ÂºÂ·c ch&acirc;n gi&ograve;. C&uacute;ng ngÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»ï¿½i mÃ¡Â»â€ºi mÃ¡ÂºÂ¥t chÃ¡Â»â€° d&ugrave;ng x&ocirc;i trÃ¡ÂºÂ¯ng v&agrave; mÃ¡Â»â„¢t quÃ¡ÂºÂ£ trÃ¡Â»Â©ng luÃ¡Â»â„¢c.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>CÃ¡Â»â€” TÃ¡ÂºÂ¿t<span id="B.E1.BB.AFa_.C4.83n_gia_.C4.91.C3.ACnh_Vi.E1.BB.87t_Nam_truy.E1.BB.81n_th.E1.BB.91ng" class="mw-headline"> <br /></span></h3>\r\n<p>CÃ¡Â»â€” tÃ¡ÂºÂ¿t truyÃ¡Â»ï¿½n thÃ¡Â»â€˜ng rÃ¡ÂºÂ¥t cÃ¡ÂºÂ§u kÃ¡Â»Â³, m&acirc;m cÃ¡Â»â€” cÃ†Â¡ bÃ¡ÂºÂ£n thÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»ï¿½ng l&agrave; 5 b&aacute;t: b&oacute;ng, miÃ¡ÂºÂ¿n, mÃ„Æ’ng, mÃ¡Â»ï¿½c, chim hoÃ¡ÂºÂ·c g&agrave; tÃ¡ÂºÂ§n v&agrave; 5 Ã„â€˜Ã„Â©a: gi&ograve;, chÃ¡ÂºÂ£, g&agrave; hoÃ¡ÂºÂ·c vÃ¡Â»â€¹t luÃ¡Â»â„¢c, nÃ¡Â»â„¢m, x&agrave;o. Ng&agrave;y nay m&acirc;m cÃ¡Â»â€” tÃ¡ÂºÂ¿t Ã„â€˜&atilde; c&oacute; nhiÃ¡Â»ï¿½u thay Ã„â€˜Ã¡Â»â€¢i vÃ¡Â»ï¿½ thÃ¡Â»Â±c Ã„â€˜Ã†Â¡n theo xu hÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»â€ºng tinh giÃ¡ÂºÂ£n, ch&uacute; trÃ¡Â»ï¿½ng "chÃ†Â¡i" hÃ†Â¡n "Ã„Æ’n".</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb06864644_square.jpg', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb06864644_thumbnail.jpg', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb06864644_small.jpg', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb06864644_crop.jpg', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb06864644_medium.jpg', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb06864644_large.jpg', 'active', 1, '14:49:59', 1, 'admin', '15:42:49', 1, 'admin', 1, 'admin', '14:50:12', 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 'vi_VN');
INSERT INTO news_article (article_id, category_id, title, sub_title, slug, description, content, author, icons, image_square, image_thumbnail, image_small, image_crop, image_medium, image_large, status, num_views, created_date, created_user_id, created_user_name, updated_date, updated_user_id, updated_user_name, activate_user_id, activate_user_name, activate_date, allow_comment, num_comments, is_hot, ordering, show_date, sticky, language) VALUES (15, 1, 'Halong Bay', '', 'halong-bay', '<p>Ha Long Bay (literally: "Descending Dragon Bay"; Vietnamese: VÃ¡Â»â€¹nh HÃ¡ÂºÂ¡ Long) is a UNESCO World Heritage Site, and a popular travel destination, located in QuÃ¡ÂºÂ£ng Ninh province, Vietnam.</p>', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Administratively, the bay belongs to Ha Long City, CÃ¡ÂºÂ©m PhÃ¡ÂºÂ£ town, and part of Van Don district. The bay features thousands of limestone karsts and isles in various sizes and shapes. Ha Long Bay is a center of a larger zone which includes B&aacute;i TÃ¡Â»Â­ Long bay to the northeast, and C&aacute;t B&agrave; islands to the southwest. These larger zones share similar geological, geographical, geomorphological, climate, and cultural characters.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb60b67f10_crop.JPG" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>The Kissing Rocks</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ha Long Bay has an area of around 1,553km2, including 1,960 islets, most of which are limestone. The core of the bay has an area of 334km2 with a high density of 775 islets. The limestone in this bay has gone through 500 million years of formation in different conditions and environments. The evolution of the karst in this bay has taken 20 million years under the impact of the tropical wet climate. The geo-diversity of the environment in the area has created biodiversity, including a tropical evergreen biosystem, oceanic and sea shore biosystem. Ha Long Bay is home to 14 endemic floral species and 60 endemic faunal species.<br /><br />Historical research surveys have shown the presence of prehistorical human beings in this area tens of thousands years ago. The successive ancient cultures are the Soi NhÃ¡Â»Â¥ culture around 18,000-7,000 BC, the C&aacute;i B&egrave;o culture 7,000-5,000 BC and the HÃ¡ÂºÂ¡ Long culture 3,500-5,000 years ago. Ha Long Bay also marked important events in the history of Vietnam with many artifacts found in B&agrave;i ThÃ†Â¡ Mout, Ã„ï¿½Ã¡ÂºÂ§u GÃ¡Â»â€” Cave, B&atilde;i Ch&aacute;y.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb60a1bf5b_crop.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Thien Cung grotto</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><br />500 years ago, Nguyen Trai praised the beauty of Ha Long Bay in his verse LÃ¡Â»â„¢ nhÃ¡ÂºÂ­p V&acirc;n Ã„ï¿½Ã¡Â»â€œn, in which he called it "rock wonder in the sky".In 1962, the Ministry of Culture, Sports and Tourism of Vietnam listed Ha Long Bay in the National Relics and Landscapes publication.In 1994, the core zone of Ha Long Bay was listed by UNESCO as a World Heritage Site according to criteria vii, and listed for a second time according to criteria viii.</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb69b56214_square.jpg', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb69b56214_thumbnail.jpg', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb69b56214_small.jpg', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb69b56214_crop.jpg', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb69b56214_medium.jpg', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7cb69b56214_large.jpg', 'active', 1, '15:00:37', 1, 'admin', '15:07:34', 1, 'admin', 1, 'admin', '15:00:47', 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 'en_US');
INSERT INTO news_article (article_id, category_id, title, sub_title, slug, description, content, author, icons, image_square, image_thumbnail, image_small, image_crop, image_medium, image_large, status, num_views, created_date, created_user_id, created_user_name, updated_date, updated_user_id, updated_user_name, activate_user_id, activate_user_name, activate_date, allow_comment, num_comments, is_hot, ordering, show_date, sticky, language) VALUES (16, 13, 'VÃ¡Â»â€¹nh HÃ¡ÂºÂ¡ Long', '', 'vinh-ha-long', '<p>VÃ¡Â»â€¹nh HÃ¡ÂºÂ¡ Long (vÃ¡Â»â€¹nh nÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»â€ºc nÃ†Â¡i rÃ¡Â»â€œng Ã„â€˜&aacute;p xuÃ¡Â»â€˜ng) l&agrave; mÃ¡Â»â„¢t vÃ¡Â»â€¹nh nhÃ¡Â»ï¿½ thuÃ¡Â»â„¢c phÃ¡ÂºÂ§n bÃ¡Â»ï¿½ T&acirc;y vÃ¡Â»â€¹nh BÃ¡ÂºÂ¯c BÃ¡Â»â„¢ tÃ¡ÂºÂ¡i khu vÃ¡Â»Â±c biÃ¡Â»Æ’n Ã„ï¿½&ocirc;ng BÃ¡ÂºÂ¯c ViÃ¡Â»â€¡t Nam, bao gÃ¡Â»â€œm v&ugrave;ng biÃ¡Â»Æ’n Ã„â€˜Ã¡ÂºÂ£o thuÃ¡Â»â„¢c th&agrave;nh phÃ¡Â»â€˜ HÃ¡ÂºÂ¡ Long, thÃ¡Â»â€¹ x&atilde; CÃ¡ÂºÂ©m PhÃ¡ÂºÂ£ v&agrave; mÃ¡Â»â„¢t phÃ¡ÂºÂ§n cÃ¡Â»Â§a huyÃ¡Â»â€¡n Ã„â€˜Ã¡ÂºÂ£o V&acirc;n Ã„ï¿½Ã¡Â»â€œn.</p>', '<p style="text-align: justify;">L&agrave; trung t&acirc;m cÃ¡Â»Â§a mÃ¡Â»â„¢t khu vÃ¡Â»Â±c rÃ¡Â»â„¢ng lÃ¡Â»â€ºn c&oacute; nhÃ¡Â»Â¯ng yÃ¡ÂºÂ¿u tÃ¡Â»â€˜ &iacute;t nhiÃ¡Â»ï¿½u tÃ†Â°Ã†Â¡ng Ã„â€˜Ã¡Â»â€œng vÃ¡Â»ï¿½ Ã„â€˜Ã¡Â»â€¹a chÃ¡ÂºÂ¥t, Ã„â€˜Ã¡Â»â€¹a mÃ¡ÂºÂ¡o, cÃ¡ÂºÂ£nh quan, kh&iacute; hÃ¡ÂºÂ­u v&agrave; vÃ„Æ’n h&oacute;a, vÃ¡Â»â€ºi vÃ¡Â»â€¹nh B&aacute;i TÃ¡Â»Â­ Long ph&iacute;a Ã„ï¿½&ocirc;ng BÃ¡ÂºÂ¯c v&agrave; quÃ¡ÂºÂ§n Ã„â€˜Ã¡ÂºÂ£o C&aacute;t B&agrave; ph&iacute;a T&acirc;y Nam, vÃ¡Â»â€¹nh HÃ¡ÂºÂ¡ Long giÃ¡Â»â€ºi hÃ¡ÂºÂ¡n trong diÃ¡Â»â€¡n t&iacute;ch khoÃ¡ÂºÂ£ng 1.553km&sup2; bao gÃ¡Â»â€œm 1.960 h&ograve;n Ã„â€˜Ã¡ÂºÂ£o lÃ¡Â»â€ºn nhÃ¡Â»ï¿½, phÃ¡ÂºÂ§n lÃ¡Â»â€ºn l&agrave; Ã„â€˜Ã¡ÂºÂ£o Ã„â€˜&aacute; v&ocirc;i, trong Ã„â€˜&oacute; v&ugrave;ng l&otilde;i cÃ¡Â»Â§a VÃ¡Â»â€¹nh c&oacute; diÃ¡Â»â€¡n t&iacute;ch 334km&sup2; quÃ¡ÂºÂ§n tÃ¡Â»Â¥ d&agrave;y Ã„â€˜Ã¡ÂºÂ·c 775 h&ograve;n Ã„â€˜Ã¡ÂºÂ£o[. LÃ¡Â»â€¹ch sÃ¡Â»Â­ kiÃ¡ÂºÂ¿n tÃ¡ÂºÂ¡o Ã„â€˜Ã¡Â»â€¹a chÃ¡ÂºÂ¥t Ã„â€˜&aacute; v&ocirc