er;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>TÃ¡ÂºÂ¿t Trung Thu c&oacute; nguÃ¡Â»â€œn gÃ¡Â»â€˜c vÃ„Æ’n minh n&ocirc;ng nghiÃ¡Â»â€¡p cÃ¡Â»Â§a d&acirc;n tÃ¡Â»â„¢c ViÃ¡Â»â€¡t. ThÃ¡Â»ï¿½i Ã„â€˜iÃ¡Â»Æ’m n&agrave;y kh&iacute; trÃ¡Â»ï¿½i m&aacute;t mÃ¡ÂºÂ», m&ugrave;a m&agrave;ng Ã„â€˜ang chÃ¡Â»ï¿½ thu hoÃ¡ÂºÂ¡ch. N&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n nghÃ¡Â»â€° ngÃ†Â¡i v&agrave; vui chÃ†Â¡i sau mÃ¡Â»â„¢t vÃ¡Â»Â¥ m&ugrave;a. Sau n&agrave;y ngÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»ï¿½i Trung Hoa tiÃ¡ÂºÂ¿p nhÃ¡ÂºÂ­n tÃ¡Â»Â« vÃ„Æ’n h&oacute;a ViÃ¡Â»â€¡t v&agrave; tiÃ¡ÂºÂ¿p Ã„â€˜&oacute; phÃ¡Â»â€¢ biÃ¡ÂºÂ¿n th&agrave;nh ng&agrave;y lÃ¡Â»â€¦ truyÃ¡Â»ï¿½n thÃ¡Â»â€˜ng cÃ¡Â»Â§a d&acirc;n tÃ¡Â»â„¢c Ã„ï¿½&ocirc;ng &Aacute; nhÃ†Â° H&agrave;n QuÃ¡Â»â€˜c, NhÃ¡ÂºÂ­t BÃ¡ÂºÂ£n.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce10ebf455_crop.JPG" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>C&aacute;c loÃ¡ÂºÂ¡i Ã„â€˜&egrave;n lÃ¡Â»â€œng</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Theo phong tÃ¡Â»Â¥c ngÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»ï¿½i ViÃ¡Â»â€¡t, v&agrave;o dÃ¡Â»â€¹p TÃ¡ÂºÂ¿t Trung Thu, cha mÃ¡ÂºÂ¹ b&agrave;y cÃ¡Â»â€” cho c&aacute;c con Ã„â€˜Ã¡Â»Æ’ mÃ¡Â»Â«ng trung thu, mua v&agrave; l&agrave;m Ã„â€˜Ã¡Â»Â§ thÃ¡Â»Â© lÃ¡Â»â€œng Ã„â€˜&egrave;n thÃ¡ÂºÂ¯p bÃ¡ÂºÂ±ng nÃ¡ÂºÂ¿n Ã„â€˜Ã¡Â»Æ’ treo trong nh&agrave; v&agrave; Ã„â€˜Ã¡Â»Æ’ c&aacute;c con rÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»â€ºc Ã„â€˜&egrave;n. CÃ¡Â»â€” mÃ¡Â»Â«ng trung thu gÃ¡Â»â€œm b&aacute;nh Trung Thu, kÃ¡ÂºÂ¹o, m&iacute;a, bÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»Å¸i v&agrave; c&aacute;c thÃ¡Â»Â© hoa quÃ¡ÂºÂ£ kh&aacute;c nÃ¡Â»Â¯a. Ã„ï¿½&acirc;y l&agrave; dÃ¡Â»â€¹p Ã„â€˜Ã¡Â»Æ’ cha mÃ¡ÂºÂ¹ t&ugrave;y theo khÃ¡ÂºÂ£ nÃ„Æ’ng kinh tÃ¡ÂºÂ¿ gia Ã„â€˜&igrave;nh thÃ¡Â»Æ’ hiÃ¡Â»â€¡n t&igrave;nh thÃ†Â°Ã†Â¡ng y&ecirc;u con c&aacute;i mÃ¡Â»â„¢t c&aacute;ch cÃ¡Â»Â¥ thÃ¡Â»Æ’. V&igrave; thÃ¡ÂºÂ¿, t&igrave;nh y&ecirc;u gia Ã„â€˜&igrave;nh lÃ¡ÂºÂ¡i c&agrave;ng khÃ¡ÂºÂ¯ng kh&iacute;t th&ecirc;m. CÃ…Â©ng trong dÃ¡Â»â€¹p n&agrave;y ngÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»ï¿½i ta mua b&aacute;nh trung thu, tr&agrave;, rÃ†Â°Ã¡Â»Â£u Ã„â€˜Ã¡Â»Æ’ c&uacute;ng tÃ¡Â»â€¢ ti&ecirc;n, biÃ¡ÂºÂ¿u &ocirc;ng b&agrave;, cha mÃ¡ÂºÂ¹, thÃ¡ÂºÂ§y c&ocirc;, bÃ¡ÂºÂ¡n b&egrave;, hÃ¡Â»ï¿½ h&agrave;ng v&agrave; c&aacute;c &acirc;n nh&acirc;n kh&aacute;c.</p>', 'Wikipedia', '', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce10ebf455_square.JPG', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce10ebf455_thumbnail.JPG', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce10ebf455_small.JPG', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce10ebf455_crop.JPG', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce10ebf455_medium.JPG', 'http://localhost/amancms/upload/news/admin/2010/08/4c7ce10ebf455_large.JPG', 'active', 1, '18:03:29', 1, 'admin', '18:23:35', 1, 'admin', 1, 'admin', '18:03:40', 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, 'vi_VN');


